Introduction

Im Siu is a South Korean trainee.

In 2019, he was a contestant on MNET's survival show Produce X 101 but left the show before the reevaluation grade in episode 2.

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7 starting in October 2024.
